extendedInfo.description: Welcome to the App for Dextress Hair Face BodyLocated at Murrumba Downs, Dextress Hair Face Body salon is located conveniently on Dohles Rocks Rd, in the Castle Hill Shopping Court. Spread over 2 shop fronts the interior mixes tranquil and earthy tones. We offer a sense of warmth and relaxation in our friendly surroundings. We welcome our guests with the utmost comfort and client focus. We endeavour to fulfil your hair & beauty needs and create an everlasting memorable experience. Our dedicated team will personalise your experience with their total attention and professional knowledge to achieve the best results for you. Download our App to access all of our promotions, offers and news. Make appointments, order Gift Vouchers and receive up to the minute notifications direct to your phone!
